## Implementation Notes

### Architecture
- Build on `DepthEffect` base class from P3-VD35
- Integrate with `MLGPUEngine` and `StyleTransferEngine` from VJlive-2
- Implement neural style transfer using pre-trained models (AdaIN, FastStyle, CycleGAN)
- Add depth-driven style strength modulation
- Support async inference with CUDA streams
- Implement style image preprocessing and caching

### Performance Optimizations
- Use TensorRT for optimized inference
- Implement async CUDA streams for non-blocking execution
- Use mixed precision (FP16) for speed
- Cache style features for consistent application

### Memory Management
- Style model: ~100-500MB per model
- Style features: variable size depending on model
- Output buffer: H × W × 3 bytes
- Profile GPU memory, enforce gpu_memory_limit
- Free unused models from cache

### Safety Rails
- Enforce style_strength 0-1, content_weight 0-1
- Clamp gpu_memory_limit to [1.0, 8.0]
- Validate style_model and depth_style_mapping
- Fallback to CPU inference if GPU unavailable

